File Name		: 05-Primitives.tar.gz
Binary Size		: 8.6K
Design Computer		: Celeron 2.4Ghz , 512MB Ram, Fedora Core 4
Date Released		: 2005/04/04

Environment		: Unix / Linux

INSTRUCTIONS :
---------------

1) Extract zip file
2) Type "make" to compile
3) Type "./main" to run

